      "review_summary": "The PR prepends resolved `messages.responsePrefix` to `message(action=send)` outbound text, resolves identity templates, skips prefixes with unresolved placeholders, and adds focused core-send tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +37, Tests +140. Total +177 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Source inspection shows current main and the latest release build message-tool send text without `responsePrefix`, while Mantis baseline/candidate proof demonstrates the static-prefix failure and candidate behavior in Telegram.",
